headline: Affiliated Managers (AMG) Surges 3.6%: Is This an Indication of Further Gains?
summary: Affiliated Managers (AMG) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock suggests that there could be more strength down the road.
